Package ui.menu

Class TextBox.KeyHandler.MovementKeyHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.input.MovementKeyHandler
      • ui.menu.TextBox.KeyHandler.MovementKeyHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyHandler
    Enclosing class:
    TextBox.KeyHandler
    private class TextBox.KeyHandler.MovementKeyHandler
extends MovementKeyHandler
    Used to detect leaving the text box edit mode.
    A key handler that translates key presses into movement directions. Also detects enter, space, and escape keys.
